summary: WHILE TRAVELING AT 55MPH THE HOOD RELEASED HITTING THE ROOF ABOVE THE WINDSHIELD.  CAUSED DAMAGE TO THE ROOF, THE HOOD AND THE FENDERS.  NOTE THAT THE HOD HAD NOT BEEN OPENED FOR OVER A MONTH.  ALSO NOTE THAT THE HOOD WAS IN THE FULLY CLOSED POSITION BEFORE STARTING OUT ON THE ROAD ON 11/20/2015.
